# Countering an offer

TaskRabbit allows Task posters to counter offers.
You can set the charge price and the comments.


### POST /api/v1/tasks/1452/offers/213/counter

```
{
  "charge_price": 30,
  "comments": "This is more fair."
}
```


### Simplified Response


```
{
  "id":214,
  "charge_price": 30,
  "state": "made",
  "comments": "This is more fair.",
  "task": {
    "name": "My Task",
    "named_price": 10,
    "state": "opened",
    "geography": {
      "id": 1052,
      "name": "Boston"
    }
  }
}
```

